     fhir:div [ fhir:v "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: MedicationStatement bb2d0be6-24fd-4e1f-8fa4-10e058ed2775</b></p><a name=\"bb2d0be6-24fd-4e1f-8fa4-10e058ed2775\"> </a><a name=\"hcbb2d0be6-24fd-4e1f-8fa4-10e058ed2775\"> </a><div style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: #d9e0e7; padding: 6px; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid #8da1b4; border-radius: 5px; line-height: 60%\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\"/><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Profiles: <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/ipa/STU1.1/StructureDefinition-ipa-medicationstatement.html\">IPA-MedicationStatement</a> version: 1.1.0, <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/ips/STU2/StructureDefinition-MedicationStatement-uv-ips.html\">MedicationStatement (IPS)</a>, <a href=\"http://hl7.eu/fhir/base/2.0.0/StructureDefinition-medicationStatement-eu-core.html\">MedicationStatement (EU core)</a>, <a href=\"https://build.fhir.org/ig/hl7-eu/eps/StructureDefinition-MedicationStatement-eu-eps.html\">MedicationStatement (EPS)</a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Security Labels: <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/v3/ObservationValue/cs.html\">device reported (Details: v3 Code System ObservationValue code DEVRPT = 'device reported')</a>, <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/v3/ObservationValue/cs.html\">patient reported (Details: v3 Code System ObservationValue code PATRPT = 'patient reported')</a>, <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/v3/ObservationValue/cs.html\">syntactic transform (Details: v3 Code System ObservationValue code SYNTAC = 'syntactic transform')</a>, <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/v3/ObservationValue/cs.html\">mapped (Details: v3 Code System ObservationValue code MAPPED = 'mapped')</a>, <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/v3/ObservationValue/cs.html\">patient asserted (Details: v3 Code System ObservationValue code PATAST = 'patient asserted')</a></p></div><p><b>basedOn</b>: <a href=\"Bundle-IpsBundle.html#urn-uuid-847b849a-eb83-4387-b60b-46eb8d39ebfd\">Prescription for Insulin Novorapid</a></p><p><b>status</b>: Active</p><p><b>category</b>: <span title=\"Codes:{http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/medication-statement-category community}, {http://snomed.info/sct 360270004}\">Active ambulatory use</span></p><p><b>medication</b>: <a href=\"Bundle-IpsBundle.html#urn-uuid-e6f153f4-6188-4dc4-9f19-f4179b9ee720\">Insulin NovoRapid 100 units/ml</a></p><p><b>subject</b>: <a href=\"Bundle-IpsBundle.html#urn-uuid-b4ac89c5-6589-417f-beef-d3fb1ef9c70f\">Mikael Rinnetmäki</a></p><p><b>effective</b>: 2023-10-06 --&gt; (ongoing)</p><p><b>informationSource</b>: <a href=\"Bundle-IpsBundle.html#urn-uuid-b4ac89c5-6589-417f-beef-d3fb1ef9c70f\">Mikael Rinnetmäki, the patient</a></p><p><b>reasonCode</b>: <span title=\"Codes:{http://snomed.info/sct 46635009}, {http://hl7.org/fhir/sid/icd-10 E10}\">Type 1 diabetes mellitus</span></p><p><b>reasonReference</b>: <a href=\"Bundle-IpsBundle.html#urn-uuid-1558c456-efa1-4b3d-abe2-1522c6048bc7\">Type 1 diabetes mellitus</a></p><p><b>note</b>: By urn:uuid:b4ac89c5-6589-417f-beef-d3fb1ef9c70f</p><blockquote><div><p>My prescription is for 50 - 100 iU/d. I usually consume 40 to 70 iU per day.</p>\n</div></blockquote><blockquote><p><b>dosage</b></p><p><b>text</b>: 40-70 iU/d</p><p><b>patientInstruction</b>: 50-100 yksikköä vuorokaudessa, Pumpcart säiliöt insuliinipumppuun ihon alle DMI</p><h3>DoseAndRates</h3><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td style=\"display: none\">-</td><td><b>Rate[x]</b></td></tr><tr><td style=\"display: none\">*</td><td>40-70 units per day</td></tr></table></blockquote></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
